summary:
An accomplished Senior Level Management Professional with in excess of 10 years’ experience across diversified organisational clusters in Sales, Commercial, & Marketing. 
Furthermore offering cross-cultural experience and global footprint exposure in all aspects of: General and Operations Management [Regional, National and Continental] | Project and Procurement Management | Business Turnaround, Strategy Planning and Implementation | Capacity and Stakeholder Relations | Leadership, Guidance and Mentoring | Training and Skills Development. Possesses a forward-thinking ability to build strategic partnerships by lucratively concluding complex  deals across Africa.

+5 Years of Sales Management Experience
+5 Years of expansion projects in Africa, including West, Central and East.
